    The SqlTestLoader loads the test files that should be run by the Ksql testing tool based on a path and optional filters.

    Represents a tuple of (test name, file, test statements) that constitute a ksql test.

    The SqlTestReader is an iterator over a test case that will return one test statement to execute at a time.
